muros (0.9.6) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Fork (OPNsense-on-Debian) supersedes the legacy FastAPI product.
  * System config now owned by the package: php-fpm pool (no more
    silent reset to max_children=5) and sysctl forwarding.
  * auth: port local account synchronization to Debian tooling (getent,
    userdel/groupdel, root/nogroup groups) instead of FreeBSD pw.
  * themes: restyle the sidebar header (left-aligned logo, version label,
    compact user and logout row).

 -- MurOS <dev@muros.org>  Fri, 19 Jun 2026 21:15:00 +0200

